4. Data Binding

    4.1 One way Binding
        4.1.1 From Component to View
            4.1.1.1 String Interpolation / Interpolation - syntax : {{expression}}
            4.1.1.2 Property Binding  - syntax: [binding-target] = "binding-source"
        4.1.2 From View to Component
            4.1.2.1 Event Binding - syntax : (eventName)="function call"
            4.1.2.2 Event Binding using $event - (eventName)="function call($event)"
            4.1.2.3 Event Binding using template referrencing - syntax : #template-referencing-variable
    4.2 Two way Binding
        4.2.1 ngModel = FormsModule. syntax: [(ngModel)]="property-name"

